  {
    "key": "80ed9beb097477b8bfacd894c6233b62abb3891c82cf0db72cd27c30b4351695",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_03.png[/img]{%cultist% steps forward, brandishing his scarred pate for all the strangers to see. They nod and bow, and their leader speaks with his eyes to the sands.%SPEECH_ON%Davkul has spoken.%SPEECH_OFF%Nodding, %cultist% responds.%SPEECH_ON%And to every word I listen.%SPEECH_OFF%The leader retrieves a strange blade seemingly out of nowhere and runs it across his fingers. He speaks again without looking up.%SPEECH_ON%Then do as he requests.%SPEECH_OFF% %cultist% takes the blade and nods.%SPEECH_ON%Davkul awaits us all.%SPEECH_OFF%The strange men collapse to the ground and put their faces into the sand. Their chests rise and fall, tremor, and then they move no more. They have drowned themselves into the desert herself. %cultist% returns carrying a bizarre dagger with him.}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_03.png[/img]{%cultist% steps forward, brandishing his scarred pate for all the strangers to see. They nod and bow, and their leader speaks with his eyes to the sands.%SPEECH_ON%Davkul has spoken.%SPEECH_OFF%Nodding, %cultist% responds.%SPEECH_ON%And to every word I listen.%SPEECH_OFF%The leader retrieves a strange blade seemingly out of nowhere and runs it across his fingers. He speaks again without looking up.%SPEECH_ON%Then do as he requests.%SPEECH_OFF% %cultist% takes the blade and nods.%SPEECH_ON%Davkul awaits us all.%SPEECH_OFF%The strange men collapse to the ground and put their faces into the sand. Their chests rise and fall, tremor, and then they move no more. They have drowned themselves into the desert herself. %cultist% returns carrying a bizarre dagger with him.}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "41ef6d0eb16b8015e905fee1f11b909f9c8a48da2824c1ed97036e95dad70c23",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_03.png[/img]{You come over a sand dune to see a half dozen men. They are wearing black cloaks and have their sleeve-sheathed hands holding onto one another to form a complete circle. Despite every one of their heads being down, they all seem to sense your presence and turn to stare. One man lets his hands go and steps forward.%SPEECH_ON%Davkul awaits us all, traveler, even the gilded path permits his patience.%SPEECH_OFF%}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_03.png[/img]{You come over a sand dune to see a half dozen men. They are wearing black cloaks and have their sleeve-sheathed hands holding onto one another to form a complete circle. Despite every one of their heads being down, they all seem to sense your presence and turn to stare. One man lets his hands go and steps forward.%SPEECH_ON%Davkul awaits us all, traveler, even the gilded path permits his patience.%SPEECH_OFF%}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7622c0ec36fdeba90c8f03ce07f4ff3e7d7c578b7fcd06c9a846eda259386872",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_03.png[/img]{You offer a modest hello and goodbye to the black cloaks, then move on. They do not resist you, nor call out to you in any manner. The last you see of them they are holding hands again and have their heads crooned forward and staring into the sands. There is not a single jug of water or basket of food anywhere to be seen. If they had not come here to die, what could possibly save them?}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_03.png[/img]{You offer a modest hello and goodbye to the black cloaks, then move on. They do not resist you, nor call out to you in any manner. The last you see of them they are holding hands again and have their heads crooned forward and staring into the sands. There is not a single jug of water or basket of food anywhere to be seen. If they had not come here to die, what could possibly save them?}\""
  },
  {
